videos.description: Lindell Wigginton grabs a lob pass from Marial Shayok and adjusts it mid-air for the layup.
videos.headline: Wigginton makes adjustment mid-air during layup

videos.description: A missed shot by the Red Raiders leads to an alley-oop from Tyrese Haliburton to George Conditt IV.
videos.headline: Texas Tech missed shot leads to Iowa State alley-oop

videos.description: Kyler Edwards makes the tough layup through contact and gets the foul.
videos.headline: Texas Tech's Edwards makes tough layup

videos.description: Texas Tech's Jarrett Culver uses a sweet Eurostep for a layup to tie the game at 61-61 vs. Iowa State.
videos.headline: Culver's Eurostep for layup sends crowd into frenzy
